Sentencas: In this work, double perovskite-type oxide PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+delta (PBSCF) is synthesized by the conventional wet chemical method and firstly characterized as the oxygen electrode for reversible solid oxide electrochemical cells (RSOCs).
Titulo: Preparation and properties of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ as novel oxygen electrode for reversible solid oxide electrochemical cell

Sentencas: The microstructure and electrochemical performance of RSOCs based on this oxygen electrode are investigated.
Titulo: Preparation and properties of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ as novel oxygen electrode for reversible solid oxide electrochemical cell

Sentencas: The maximum power density of the cell reaches 986 mW/cm(2) at 800 degrees C and the cell has good stability in short-term test in fuel cell (SOFC) mode.
Titulo: Preparation and properties of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ as novel oxygen electrode for reversible solid oxide electrochemical cell

Sentencas: In electrolysis cell (SOEC) mode, it displays an electrolysis current density as high as 1.3 A/cm(2) when the temperature, absolute humidity (AH) and applied voltage are 800 degrees C, 50 vol % and 1.3 V, respectively.
Titulo: Preparation and properties of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ as novel oxygen electrode for reversible solid oxide electrochemical cell

Sentencas: The cells also exhibit excellent durability of 120 h in SOEC mode and present good reversibility.
Titulo: Preparation and properties of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ as novel oxygen electrode for reversible solid oxide electrochemical cell

Sentencas: The results suggest that the RSOCs based on this oxygen electrode has a very promising prospect.
Titulo: Preparation and properties of PrBa0.5Sr0.5Co1.5Fe0.5O5+δ as novel oxygen electrode for reversible solid oxide electrochemical cell
